<h4 id="rest原理" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#rest原理" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Rest原理</h4>
<blockquote>
<p>WebMvcAutoConfiguration：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>请求过来被</strong> HiddenHttpMethodFilter 拦截</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code>	<span class="token annotation punctuation">@Bean</span>
