<p>SpringBoot默认是禁用了矩阵变量的功能</p>
<p>手动开启：对于路径的处理，由 <code v-pre>UrlPathHelper</code> 进行解析</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"></div></div></li>
