<p><strong>使用示例：</strong></p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code>    <span class="token annotation punctuation">@GetMapping</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"/params"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
